    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Axis Bank Asia Pacific Associates. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Risk Analyst to strengthen our Jaipur-based team.\n\nAbout Axis Bank Asia Pacific Associates:\nAxis Bank Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Axis Bank Asia Pacific Associates!",
